# Optional: enables "date added to playlist" enrichment for unavailable videos.
# Get a free YouTube Data API v3 key: https://console.cloud.google.com
#   1. Create/select a project  2. Enable "YouTube Data API v3"
#   3. Credentials -> Create credentials -> API key  4. (Recommended) restrict it to that API
# Then copy this file to .env and paste your key below. Without it, PLDL works fine;
# you just won't get the playlist date-added signal.
YOUTUBE_API_KEY=
